text: KAGE may refer to: * KHWK (AM), a radio station (1380 AM) licensed to serve Winona, Minnesota, United States, which held the call sign KAGE from 1957 to 2019 * KGSL, a radio station (95.3 FM) licensed to serve Winona, Minnesota, which held the call sign KAGE-FM until 2015 * KAGE: Alternative Game Engine, a free and open-source game engine * Shadow of the Ninja, a video game
title: KAGE
